<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Alison </PERSON> <PERSON> Smale </PERSON>, <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION>'s chief of bureau for much of <LOCATION> Eastern </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Europe </LOCATION>, covered the <LOCATION> Soviet </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Union </LOCATION> for four years.
