<FIRST>r a PM-BuildingCollapse     06-02 0322</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Building Collapse,0335</SECOND>
<HEAD>Store Collapses around Owner's Wife</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ZANESVILLE, Ohio (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
