<TEXT>
 EDITOR'S NOTE: <PERSON> Bryan </PERSON> <PERSON> Brumley </PERSON>, a national security writer based in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>, was an <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> correspondent in <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION> in 1981-82 and has covered previous summits in <LOCATION> Reykjavik </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Iceland </LOCATION>, and <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
