ailed to demonstrate that the attorney general has acted in bad faith,'' the judge said, therefore he had no power to overrule the <ORGANIZATION> INS </ORGANIZATION> decision to keep <PERSON> Bosch </PERSON> in custody. His deportation case now goes to the regional commissioner of the <ORGANIZATION> INS </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Dallas </LOCATION> for a recommendation.
