t after flying to <LOCATION> Boston </LOCATION> from <LOCATION> Arizona </LOCATION>. Mrs. <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON> disclosed last year that she had been addicted to amphetamines for 26 years until she entered a <LOCATION> Minnesota </LOCATION> clinic in 1982. She said she began taking the pills to curb her appetite and became addicted.
