ay rent, do n't have to pay for lights,'' he said. `` I'm comfortable here.'' <PERSON> Ouimet </PERSON> said he plans to continue his correspondence with <PERSON> Mother </PERSON> <PERSON> Teresa </PERSON> after her visit, adding that it has `` broadened'' his outlook. He hopes his fellow inmates will have the same experience when they meet her Saturday. `` We are poor in spirit, poor in emotion and poor in material possessions but in the eyes of our Father we have a great dignity,'' he said.
